{"/service/ndnp/njr/batch_njr_jackson_ver01/data/sn92059905/00513685889/1924041601/0535.xml":{"full_text":"STILL GOING STRONG- THE GREAT HAT TRICK\n1\nW HE WAS\nFUNNY AT FIRSTS\nBUT HE MAKES\nME NERVOUS\nBusiness Outlook\nBetter Than Ever\nDeclare* Wm. S. Emley, Former\nHead of Real Estate Board,\nin Statement on Real\nEstate Conditions\nBy H. C. Test\n\u201cFrom the standpoint of the\nman interested in real estate, the\noutlook for business both in At\nlantic City and on Absecon Island\nwas never better,\u201d declared Wil\nliam S. Emley, former President\nof the Atlantic City Real Estate\nBoard, prominent civic leader and\nexpert on real estate valuations\nin Atlantic City, Ventnor\" and\nother neighbor resorts. \u201cThe en\ntire Island and its business is on\nsuch a solid foundation of values\nthat there is nothing to stand in\nthe way of constant growth and\nimprovement.\n\u201cIt is my belief, and the belief\nof most men who must use real\nvision in their business, that we\nhave merely scratched our market\nfor those who should buy homes\nor enter business in Atlantic City\nToday we lie within a few hour;\nride of half the population of th(\nUnited States and we have bui\nto call attention to our advantages\nas a resort and as a residence\ncity to bring new thousands where\nMetal Garage\nFor Sale\nA galvanized iron, steel\nframe one-car garage in\nfirst-c lass serviceable\ncondition. Now in use.\nWill sell at reasonable\nprice owing to sale of\npremises.\nWrite to\nPOST OFFICE BOX 904\nor\nPHONE MARINE 4264\nhundreds have come before.\n\u201cThe job of the real estate man\nof today is to get people to come\nto Atlantic City just once. It\nwould amaze many people to learn\n.how many intending transient\nvisitors have been changed into\npermenent residents and boosters\nfor these Absecon Island resorts\non their first coming. I can\nquote instances where people have\nbeen really forced to come here on\norders of physicians because of\nthe health-giving climate, and who\nhave made their homes here ever\nsince.\n\u201cOne of the reasons why I ad\nvocate the policy of persuading\npeople to come to our resorts by\nmeans of Broadway signs or any\nother method is that their minds\nmay. be disabused of the belief\nthat we have nothing more than\na mere summer resort, something,\npossibly, to be compared to Coney\nIsland. With all the immense\narea and population which we\nhave from which to draw we\nshould be able to reach the very j\nhighest class of people. And once j\nwe get them here, they are bound j\nto be \u2018sold\u2019 on Atlantic City and\nto love it without having to be\npersuaded further.\n\u201cWe have the finest winter\nclimate in America\u2014the closing\nwinter has proved it. We have\neverything that can be enjoyed\nin the big inland city with the\nwonderful Boardwalk and so\nmany other features tha tare At\nlantic City\u2019s own. From the stand\npoint of the man interested in real\nestate, the outlook is wonderful.\nAnd we have only to work to\ngether and in harmony of pur\npose to make it better than we can\nimagine.\u201d\nTo Last Your Business On\nThe Classified Page Costs\nBut a Few Cents. It Stays\nWith The Reader For A\nWhole Week.\nFord Used Car Department\nALL. MODELS\nReconditioned, Repainted, Reasonable\nTerms If Desired\n2215 PACIFIC AVENUE\nE. H. SNEAD Ufarine 55S8-M A. M. HALL\nOpen Evenings and Sunday\nIF IT IS IN MARGATE\n\u2014Ask\u2014\nFARRINGTON\nSpecializing Margate Real Estate\nDouglass Atlantic Aves.\nMARGATE CITY, N. J.\nt NEPTUNE 876\nSPECIAL: Two Six Room Bath Bungalows with\nGarage. Between Ventnor Atlantic Avenues.\n$12,500 each. Well Financed.\nBuu\nNow-,\nThis is the Season of the\nYear when Prices\nare Lowest.\nIt is to Your Advantage\nto Stock Your Coal\nBin NOW.","height":"18424","width":"15728"}}
